Compilation
===========

In this directory to build the library just type 

    make

It is independent of the other files of Premia; 

It will compile the following model

	1) Non exploding bushy tree for the LMM


make will produce the following program: lmm_bushy_pricer

Version
=======

the compilation works under Red Hat 9 with:

	gcc (GCC) 3.2.2 20030222 (Red Hat Linux 3.2.2-5)
	glibc-2.3.2-11.9




